<p>Bolt's SVG icon system provides the ability to customize an individual icon's color (the shape itself), background color, and background opacity levels, in both the Twig and Custom Element formats the design system ships.</p>


<h2>via Web Component:</h2>

{% set customElementExample %}{%- verbatim -%}
<bolt-icon
  size="xlarge"
  background="circle"
  name="marketing-gray"
  style="
    color: #a65388;
    --bolt-theme-icon-background: #a65388;
    --bolt-theme-icon: #FFF;
    --bolt-theme-icon-background-opacity: 1;
  "></bolt-icon>
{%- endverbatim -%}{% endset %}

{% embed '@bolt-components-code-snippet/code-snippet.twig' with {
  lang: 'html',
  content: customElementExample
} %}
{% endembed %}

